First Department,

January, 2009

(January 6, 2009) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Oscar Olmeda, Appellant. [872 NYS2d 687]

Judgment, Supreme Court, New York County (James A. Yates, J.), rendered on or about September 14, 2006, unanimously affirmed. No opinion. Order filed. Concur—Lippman, P.J., Mazzarelli, Sweeny, DeGrasse and Freedman, JJ.
